{"tid":1602521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】戰後檢討及10.1行動討論","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T14:32:01.000Z","uid":198113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"438f64376e82815c33b9277f80f10f0203953625","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"望到今日咁多手足比狗拉，個心好傷，令我不禁喺度諗，究竟我哋而家做嘅嘢，係咪需要改變<br />\n<br />\n我認為依家我哋所做嘅嘢嘅代價，遠超於所帶來嘅利益<br />\n<br />\n每次我哋去打狗嘅時候，我哋又做唔到啲乜嘢，但係又會有好多嘅手足比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n一個勇武比狗拉咗，我哋就少咗一個勇武。又會有幾多個勇武，真係會咁勇敢，比人拉完之後仲會繼續出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n依家我哋已經比自己對狗嘅憤怒蒙蔽左雙眼，目標由憾動政權，變咗做打狗洩憤。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">梁天琦同我地講過：「你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋係時候要保持警覺同埋思考，將個目標轉返去正確嘅方向。因此，10.1唔可以再好似之前咁，我哋一定要設立一個明確嘅目標去憾動政權，而唔係同啲狗戀戰<br />\n<br />\n我哋就喺度一齊討論下10.1嘅行動同埋目標，等我哋送份大禮同中共賀賀壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cda8ab9311eeee441974380365f427d1cbaa091","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"即使今日好多手足比狗拉咗 我哋都唔可以氣餒"},{"pid":"0c6d5397c4902cd71791b2882f69d00a0e06861d","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"我哋一定要喺10.1做場大事比咁多位手足睇，以答謝佢哋今日所付出嘅一切"},{"pid":"e2b91e4031ff4e86debc9626a7c1cfedca06ba5a","tid":1602521,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"唔好戀戰<br />\n但狗一定要打<br />\n政權=軍權"},{"pid":"525d326aa5d33d73c118666601926ce7089f570c","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6c20e8277d78d7e811d10368ac41c6c35781e25","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b91e4031ff4e86debc9626a7c1cfedca06ba5a","tid":1602521,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"唔好戀戰<br />\n但狗一定要打<br />\n政權=軍權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"啲狗只係政權個盾，我哋只需要打穿個盾，然後再攻擊後邊嗰個政權"},{"pid":"c6b3efe34864f70a4283db829926c03345e56734","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:26:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74ce1e25afdc028f087c508170ce65db48497b6c","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce702b2bbdd3d98ecec96087e6a67ba9b0bf5292","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a780ec757c1103de9de9dbd1cf06e9b1cc4ef174","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fe9619b54700542b4da3b2caefd193e10647bfc","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a63b58dccff632023db961a4b04445b67c5bb76b","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bfbd59513cad5b504ad79e97ef7156892d22b07","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"我哋絕對唔可以氣餒 快啲一齊討論後日要做啲乜"},{"pid":"948291d9ea6030694b53c5b394f079263db0518c","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9ff5fcf887f6ef9cfc87fc0019147f4758362b9","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4072de29c9917a5bf9d8e71d66fa634496e9749","tid":1602521,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c1942bd91376f500d603b